No. 27,

Orig.

Ohio v. Kentucky.

Report of Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, with supporting briefs, to report may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Reply briefs, if any, to such exceptions may be filed within 30 days. [For earlier orders herein, see, e. g., 410 U. S. 641.]
